## Accessibility

- **Contrast minimum:** WCAG AA for body, AAA for important UI
- **Focus states:** visible, distinct, never relying on color alone
- **Hit targets:** minimum {{44 × 44 pt}} on touch
- **Motion:** respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
- {{any other accessibility commitments}}

